   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Itau SME NE CL</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1)	Increase access to finance in frontier regions with focus on smaller and middle sized companies. 2)	Assist in  the development of companies located in frontier regions of the country which are still underserved by the domestic financial markets.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project consists of a new syndicated facility to Banco Ita&#xFA; BBA, S.A, (Ita&#xFA; BBA or the Bank), the wholesale subsidiary of Ita&#xFA; Unibanco Holdings (IUH).  IUH is an existing partner to IFC and one of the largest banks in Brazil.  It offers a wide range of financial services including banking services to individuals, micro, small and medium enterprises, and large corporate clients through Ita&#xFA; BBA.  This above Project will support Ita&#xFA; BBAs lending operations in the frontier regions of Brazil, especially in the North and Northeast, assisting the Bank to grow its credit portfolio and presence in those regions.</narrative>
  </description>
